{"tid":1392671,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［全民公投］要林鄭定鄧炳強 ［推到鄧總統睇到］","createTime":"2019-07-31T23:31:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T23:43:24.000Z","uid":273760,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bd5d2aa8e605944602b3dd5538aa3a32eecb83cf","tid":1392671,"uid":273760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:31:00.000Z","msg":"鄧炳強依家根本可以控制特首<br />\n點解你唔做埋佢個位<br />\n而且你上馬係大局為重<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對警察你可以特赦 <br />\n唔好信個老虔婆會真係幫警察<br />\n誠哥都開到聲<br />\n佢成立獨立委員會係遲早既事<br />\n對市民<br />\n佢眼中釘只有林鄭<br />\n你去除佢功大於過<br />\n市民會再次接受番警察</span></span><br />\n希望大家可以公投揀出依家最合適既人帶領香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正評：鄧炳強<br />\n負評：林鄭"},{"pid":"282324eaea80ca9206fbf42050a992f5b23b80e1","tid":1392671,"uid":273760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:32:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d3d8d474a69c17338d6c2d54cc3ac6a12d240f9","tid":1392671,"uid":101803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:33:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"feb65d2535d9dc2366c1fd0076951cbc08706c38","tid":1392671,"uid":216364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:34:35.000Z","msg":"鄧生俾我個感覺真係好黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc88c7c07eb54caef32d1ae0df614d148c168ff8","tid":1392671,"uid":153311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:34:50.000Z","msg":"屌，兩條仆街都咁仆街，投唔落喎"},{"pid":"cc186010b181516ed8dd0eebb5a92cd09eae6704","tid":1392671,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:35:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母點投"},{"pid":"8b82b69d2bdbf2a101a4292f997479a429c0b30b","tid":1392671,"uid":273760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feb65d2535d9dc2366c1fd0076951cbc08706c38","tid":1392671,"uid":216364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:34:35.000Z","msg":